ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project stands on the work of many others. Particular thanks to:

- The FastAPI team for a framework that makes async Python enjoyable
- Supabase for the free-tier Postgres + RLS + Vault stack
- HuggingFace for free Space hosting for open-source projects
- Vercel for free frontend hosting
- Cloudflare for free R2 (backup storage) and email routing
- The Contributor Covenant project for the spirit of our CoC
- Every security researcher whose public write-ups informed the
  check catalog in checks/

If you should be on this list and are not, open an issue or PR.
